## This page will describe about all azure cli commands
az login
az account show --output table
az account get-access-token
az vm list
az vm get-instance-view --resource-group learning-azure --name automation
az vm get-instance-view -g learning-azure -n automation  // g-denotes resourcegroup && n- denotes name as short form
az vm list -g learning-azure -d                         //List all VMs by resource group with details.
az vm list -g learning-azure                           //List all VMs by resource group.
az vm list-sizes -l eastus                            //List the available VM sizes in the east US region
